@startuml Infyro_User_Experience_Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName SansSerif
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #EEF2FF
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #4F46E5
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #64748B
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam TitleFontSize 18
skinparam TitleFontColor #0F172A

title Infyro — User experience flow\n(for everyday personal use · no coding required)

|You|
start
:Hear about Infyro\nand open the web dashboard;

|Web dashboard|
:See your home screen\n(watchers + alerts at a glance);

if (Have a watcher yet?) then (no)
  :Tap **Create watcher**;
  :Pick a name + color;
  :Choose how it talks\n(straight / careful / friendly);
  :Choose what it watches\n(stocks, crypto, news sources);
  :Paste your own AI key\n(Groq / OpenAI / Claude)\n— your key, your control;
else (yes)
endif

:Open **Settings**;
:Link Telegram with one tap\n(opens @InfyroMarketBot);

|Telegram|
:Tap **Start** in Telegram\nto connect your account;

fork
  :Ask questions in chat\ne.g. "AAPL price?"\nor "stock prices?";
  :Get a clear answer\nfrom your watcher;
fork again
  :Watcher keeps an eye\non your markets;
  :Get an alert in Telegram\nwhen something moves;
end fork

|Web dashboard|
:Come back anytime to\npause / edit / add watchers;

stop

legend right
  |= Step |= Where |
  | Create & manage | Web dashboard |
  | Chat & alerts | Telegram |
  | AI brain | Your own API key (BYOK) |
endlegend

@enduml
